sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant View as Kegiatan View
    participant Controller as RiwayatKegiatanController
    participant AbsensiController as AdminAbsensiController
    participant Model as RiwayatKegiatan
    participant Absensi as AbsensiKegiatan

    Admin->>View: Buat Kegiatan Baru
    View->>Controller: Store Kegiatan
    Controller->>Model: Create()
    Model-->>Controller: Success

    Admin->>View: Buka Menu Absensi
    View->>AbsensiController: GET /admin/absensi/kegiatan/{id}
    AbsensiController->>Absensi: Get Peserta by Kegiatan ID
    Absensi-->>AbsensiController: Return List Peserta
    AbsensiController-->>View: Tampilkan Daftar Absensi

    Admin->>View: Validasi Kehadiran (Hadir/Tidak)
    View->>AbsensiController: PUT /admin/absensi/{id}
    AbsensiController->>Absensi: Update Status
    Absensi-->>AbsensiController: Updated
    AbsensiController-->>View: Refresh Data
